{
  "stem": "22869.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And how the skeletons really moved about on the ground, it was a miracle that a person like this can even breathe, can stay alive.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this was like the last station of where a human can say, well, this is it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If you ever get out from this kind of a position that we find ourselves now, maybe you will make it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the battle for survival went to an extent that I watched children who were near their father waiting that their parent would take the last breath so they can have their bread ration and-- and devour it.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's-- it-- what a piece of bread, what a little water meant at this particular situation in Birkenau was beyond description.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we were subjected to the most cruel, the most inhumane treatment.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what was hurting more was that fellow peers that were locked up with us did this to us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they were given all the authority and all the power to do with us whatever they wanted to.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was in a-- in a certain block.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think the block was number 13.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had a German blockalteste who was locked up even before-- in the early Hitler times, he was what they call in German a [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He used to have a triangle with a green marking on it that meant that he was a common criminal at home.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And these people were taken from Sachsenhausen, I think he came.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were made the blockalteste and the guide-- the leaders of us.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
